## ğŸš€ Installation & Usage

Since this is a **Single File Application**, no installation or build process is required.

1.  Copy the code into a file named `index.html`.
2.  Open `index.html` in any modern web browser (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, or Edge).
3.  Add your goals to the **List To Do**, hit **Start**, and begin focusing!

